data.description: Like NEW only 2-Year-Old Energy Efficient Home Loaded with Upgrades! Seller has an FHA Assumable loan at a 3.75% interest rate available to the buyer if they Qualify. Highly Desirable Floorplan Close to IAH in Porter's Mill with Community Pool. 2 Bed and 2 Full Bath Downstairs. Gameroom, Full Bath & 2 Bedrooms Upstairs. Large Open Kitchen with Island for Extra Seating Perfect for Entertaining. Washer, Dryer, Craft Ice Maker Fridge all convey. Gas Range, Tankless Water Heater, and Furnace. Backyard Patio with added Extra Slab and Electric run for Hot tub. Like-New Salt Hot-Tub can Convey. No Rear Utility Easment! Use every inch of your Backyard. Energy Efficient Dual Pane Windows, Dual Zoned A/C, and Solar Panels already installed combat high power bills. EV Charger installed in Garage. Buyer to take over solar panel contract. Ring Doorbell, Outside Security Cameras, & Window Alarms all Convey with Home.
